//Memory Game
//20 cards will be positioned facedown on the screen
//After a card is clicked it will flip to reveal its face
//The user is then able to click another card while the first card remains faceup
//If the first card and the second card are not the same, both cards will return facedown
//The user is then able to select another first card
//If the user selects a first and second card that are the same, both will remain faceup and are no longer available to be clicked
// The user will select all possible matches until there are none remaining, and will win the game





